OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FThe SNP will pursue its former Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Peter Murrell for money he
OL,8,Fstole from the party, ITV Border can
OL,9,Freveal.
OL,11,FA meeting of the SNP's National
OL,12,FExecutive Committee (NEC) on Wednesday
OL,13,Fevening agreed to a proposal by First
OL,14,FMinister John Swinney to launch legal
OL,15,Faction, two sources confirmed.
OL,17,FA confiscation order is being brought
OL,18,Fagainst Murrell by the Crown Office
OL,19,Funder proceeds of crime action, which
OL,20,Fallows authorities to seize illegally
OL,21,Fobtained assets.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FThe SNP will now apply to the courts
OL,7,Ffor a compensation order in an effort
OL,8,Fto recoup some of the cash.
OL,10,FThe process could take up to four
OL,11,Fyears, NEC members believe.
OL,13,FThe SNP will also lodge a secondary
OL,14,Fcivil action against Murrell but
OL,15,Fimmediately suspend it.
OL,17,FThis action will be used if "something
OL,18,Fgoes wrong" with the proceeds of crime
OL,19,Faction.
OL,26,@yD@]OUzD@KO]
