PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FMurrell, the estranged husband of
OL,7,Fformer first minister Nicola Sturgeon,
OL,8,Flast week admitted to embezzling more
OL,9,Fthan #400,000 from the SNP.
OL,11,FHis 12-year spending spree included a
OL,12,Fluxury motorhome, a robotic lawnmower,
OL,13,Fjewellery, computer games consoles,
OL,14,Ftoilet roll and cosmetics.
OL,16,FHe is due to be sentenced later this
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FA senior SNP source said: "This was a
OL,7,Ffull and frank discussion of the whole
OL,8,FNEC, called at the request of party
OL,9,Fleader, with members hearing directly
OL,10,Ffrom the party's solicitors and being
OL,11,Fgiven the opportunity to ask detailed
OL,12,Fquestions on the party's legal options.
OL,14,F"That in itself is testament to the
OL,15,Fstrengthening of party governance and
OL,16,Ftransparency there has been under John
OL,17,FSwinney.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,F"The NEC were unanimous in their
OL,7,Fposition that we should seek to
OL,8,Frecover the funds stolen from us by
OL,9,FPeter Murrell.
OL,11,F"While that process might take some
OL,12,Ftime, if it is successful, it will
OL,13,Fmean that money donated in good faith
OL,14,Fto the SNP will be spent how it always
OL,15,Fshould have been, on helping to secure
OL,16,FScottish independence."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@WO]
