PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FThe five-year police investigation
OL,7,Fthat caught Murrell was launched after
OL,8,Fquestions were raised about how
OL,9,F#667,000 of "ring fenced" donations
OL,10,Ffor a second independence referendum
OL,11,Fcampaign was spent.
OL,13,FMr Swinney said on Wednesday that
OL,14,Fmoney had been used for the "ongoing
OL,15,Factivities" of the SNP.
OL,17,FIn the private meeting of the NEC,
OL,18,Fwhich is the SNP's governing body,
OL,19,Fthat evening Mr Swinney proposed the
OL,20,Fparty initiate legal proceedings to be
OL,21,Fgranted compensation from Murrell.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@YO]vD@]OUwD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
