FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780672278
OL,3,CExclusive: SNP move to claim back
OL,4,Cstolen money from Murrell
OL,6,FAn NEC member said senior party
OL,7,Ffigures were "worried people (who
OL,8,Fdonated to the independence
OL,9,Ffundraisers) will ask for their money
OL,10,Fback".
OL,12,FEarlier this week, Murrell's lawyer
OL,13,Ftold Edinburgh High Court that enough
OL,14,Fof his assets had been frozen by court
OL,15,Forder to allow repayment of the sum he
OL,16,Fembezzled from the party.
OL,18,FThe SNP has been asked to comment.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@^pmqD@LpnrD@EO]
